The goal of this application is to embed / detect an invisible watermark into a PGM 
image using the "dugad" algorithm.

The following resources were used to create this code:

  Web:
    http://www.bearcave.com/misl/misl_tech/wavelets/daubechies
    http://www.cosy.sbg.ac.at/~pmeerw/Watermarking
    http://www.docstoc.com/docs/15510189/Wavelet-Based-Solutions-to-the-Digital-Image-Watermarking-Problem

  Books:
    Numerical Recipes in C, Chapter 13 Section 10 (http://www.nrbook.com/c)
    Knuth, The Art of Computer Programming, Vol 2, 3rd ed, p122

